a-id="__vue-email-text" style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:600;color:#09090b;"> Coach Watts </p><p data-id="__vue-email-text" style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px;color:#71717a;"> AI-powered endurance coaching that adapts to you. </p><p data-id="__vue-email-text" style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;color:#a1a1aa;"> You&#39;re receiving this because you registered at Coach Watts. <br> You can <a data-id="__vue-email-link" style="color:#00c16a;text-decoration:underline;" href="https://coachwatts.com/unsubscribe?token=test" target="_blank"> manage your email preferences </a> at any time. </p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
